ition-colors line-clamp-1\">托雷·苏尔（南塔）</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1 line-clamp-1\">Torre Sur</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>",
